OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWoman's bank account       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Femptied after gym locker   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fraid                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A woman has described how criminals    
OL,6, raided her gym locker, stole her wallet
OL,7, and went on an #8,000 shopping spree   
OL,8, while she was exercising.              
OL,10,FCharlotte, from west London, who did   
OL,11,Fnot want her full name published, told 
OL,12,Fthe BBC how she felt blamed by her bank
OL,13,Fand made to feel like a "criminal".    
OL,15,FShe believes thieves accessed her card 
OL,16,FPIN via the phone app, but Santander   
OL,17,Fsaid she must have disclosed it.       
OL,19,FThe bank has apologised to her and     
OL,20,Frefunded her money.                    
